{
    "text": "How \"inventions\" really happen",
    "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:53:05 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "Posted <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dave.winer.12/posts/pfbid0ozeqgB5RbPo53hFzo5MaYWqZruwem1HcKo3y69mWBKShrGUFWyhBxcvTp2C8KSqSl\">on Facebook</a> in 2014, when the EFF was fighting a patent troll who claimed to have invented podcasting. ",
            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:53:12 GMT",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "You couldn't have had podcasting without a lot of things coming together. ",
                    "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:02 GMT",
                    "flNumberedSubs": "true",
                    "subs": [
                        {
                            "text": "Networks of writers who shared links. Blogging.",
                            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:16 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "A protocol for moving links around a network. HTTP.",
                            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:23 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Something to attach links and recordings to. RSS.",
                            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:26 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "A standard format for recording. MP3.",
                            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:29 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Inexpensive, easy to use playback devices, that could hook up to all this. iPod.",
                            "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:18 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "You might argue that we still haven't gotten all the pieces needed for it to really work. But one thing is for sure, <i>none</i> of the pieces existed when the famous patent troll claims to have invented podcasting. ",
                    "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:54:45 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Maybe we should reach not for a victory but for understanding. The patent system is making decisions about technological processes it doesn't understand. No wonder it gets it so wrong.",
                    "created": "Sat, 19 Aug 2023 18:56:36 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                }
            ],
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}